  <h1>Beating Clari in a Competitive Deal</h1>
  <p class="lead">Clari wins on AI forecasting credibility. You win on time-to-value, rep engagement, and stack simplicity. Here is the exact playbook.</p>
  <div class="st">Where you win against Clari</div>
  <div class="chips"><span class="chip">Faster forecast accuracy</span><span class="chip">Better rep engagement</span><span class="chip">Simpler RevOps stack</span><span class="chip">Lower integration cost</span><span class="chip">Quicker deployment</span></div>
  <div class="st">Top objections &amp; how to handle them</div>
  <div class="objs">
    <div class="oc"><div class="oq">&ldquo;Clari's AI forecasting is best-in-class.&rdquo;</div><div class="oa">Ask what their current forecast accuracy is and how long it took to get there. Clari requires 6&ndash;9 months of clean data before the model becomes accurate. What is your comparison timeline?</div></div>
    <div class="oc"><div class="oq">&ldquo;VP Sales loves the Clari board view.&rdquo;</div><div class="oa">Get to the RevOps buyer. Ask what they spend maintaining the Clari integration today &mdash; admin overhead is a consistent pain point that finance will surface at renewal.</div></div>
    <div class="oc"><div class="oq">&ldquo;Clari is already approved by our security team.&rdquo;</div><div class="oa">Approved does not mean adopted well. Ask about actual sales rep engagement with Clari &mdash; it is a management-layer tool, rep usage is notoriously low and hard to justify at renewal.</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="bc">
    <div class="st">Battlecard: key moves in the deal</div>
    <div class="bl">
      <div class="bi"><span class="bn">1</span><span>Clari's data model requires clean CRM hygiene. Ask about their current Salesforce data quality &mdash; if it is messy, Clari's model will not work and they know it.</span></div>
      <div class="bi"><span class="bn">2</span><span>Rep engagement with Clari is low &mdash; it is a VP and RevOps tool, not a rep tool. Ask where reps actually enter pipeline data today.</span></div>
      <div class="bi"><span class="bn">3</span><span>Faster value: comparable forecasting accuracy in 60 days vs Clari's 6-month ramp. Make that comparison explicit.</span></div>
      <div class="bi"><span class="bn">4</span><span>Stack consolidation: if you replace Clari plus another point tool, the ROI story is immediate and measurable in one quarter.</span></div>
    </div>
